 The technical research question I'm exploring is comparatively small.
 First, can introducing a set of transcription factors into stem cells change
 their differentiation fate (the literature suggests yes), thus making P19
 stem cells a useful model system for serotonin receptors? If yes, I would
 then use that system to explore the effects of 5-HTR activation by different
 ligands, tracking the effect of different substrates on various markers
 of cellular activity, from immediate receptor desensitization to changes
 in gene transcription.
